I just -- I hoped that I could --

4
00:27:42.280 --> 00:27:44.270 
干嘛  催着她想起来吗
What, that you could badger her into remembering?

5
00:27:44.270 --> 00:27:45.750 
事不是这样做的
That is not how this works.

6
